name: ExtensionObservationDefinition_QualifiedValue
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.ObservationDefinition.qualifiedValue` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `ObservationDefinition.qualifiedValue` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `ObservationDefinition.qualifiedValue` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`ObservationDefinition.qualifiedValue` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `ObservationDefinition.qualifiedValue` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4B: `ObservationDefinition.qualifiedInterval` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4: `ObservationDefinition.qualifiedInterval` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `ObservationDefinition.qualifiedValue` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `ObservationDefinition.qualifiedInterval`, but has no comparisons.
